1935;;Broadway Hostess;;American;;Frank McDonald;;Winifred Shaw, Genevieve Tobin, Lyle Talbot;;musical;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Broadway_Hostess;;It is about a small town girl on her rise to stardom. But it is having problems with love. Tommy falls in love with Winnie, but he feels she is in love with her manager Lucky. Lucky claims he does not want to get married, but is in fact in love with the rich socialite Iris. While Iris's brother loses money with his gambling problem.[5]